},{"pid":"09c18c1ec4b17e254d574533c37da3a2112116aa","tid":1179082,"uid":237562,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"我試過屌啲廢老"},{"pid":"9d184bd2a1af57a83e4ce3f8d4936caf5085a488","tid":1179082,"uid":3127,"like":9,"dislike":94,"score":-85,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:17:57.000Z","msg":"試過同你差唔多情況<br />\n利申 藍絲<br />\n我果陣鬧一班大陸婆打尖 <br />\n佢地唔撚理之餘仲話返我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是我發揮女人最大武器～扮慘<br />\n有個香港姨姨即刻叫我排佢前面 <br />\n頂住班大陸婆<br />\n<br />\n真係睇下附近有冇好嘅香港人肯幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5065e519110b947944be9eb83e8f4e61dc2ffb","tid":1179082,"uid":180402,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:19:01.000Z","msg":"我都會出聲屌<br />\n但香港人令人好心淡"},{"pid":"b33418d2e3528e7684ba69fad893fa9983d02547","tid":1179082,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:20:48.000Z","msg":"我都會幫手屌"},{"pid":"02adb0cc640d592a4670ed78e5f5f55a35108be7","tid":1179082,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":81,"score":-80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"係咪香港人先咁鐘意爭第一第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個位啫"},{"pid":"37af5356ea15b17cbba50f71e6a3d895e5fa554f","tid":1179082,"uid":117894,"like":1,"dislike":31,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:43:26.000Z","msg":"我都試過，有次送女朋友上巴士，個支那音地盤佬企係隊頭想搵位聶，我都正常音量叫佢排隊。佢原本話沒，我就話唔好話著你，你直接上左啦。 之後佢就發爛渣沖上車同屌我老母。 成條隊沒人理，司機又唔理，佢一路行一路屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89ea8ae2363b719d8812673e0667f5baf69b6b5","tid":1179082,"uid":39438,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:13:42.000Z","msg":"我都試過<br />\n香港人成日話團結<br />\n去到依啲位就成碌撚咁唔幫手出聲<br />\n多一把聲，依啲撚樣收硬皮"},{"pid":"12354287a7c9d1217fcb79198061cd04b282365b","tid":1179082,"uid":133525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:24:11.000Z","msg":"報驚啦"},{"