ke":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"80bb5b9eea16b28a122232c350e6a834abef5297","tid":1179082,"uid":66221,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"02adb0cc640d592a4670ed78e5f5f55a35108be7","tid":1179082,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":81,"score":-80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"係咪香港人先咁鐘意爭第一第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個位啫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:35:37.000Z","msg":"如果佢打尖令你返工遲到冇咗份工你仲可唔可以講得出呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:51:34.000Z","msg":"應機啦三毛,死撚咗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb36b2220d99c8f453f885905fc378530d8aeb9e","tid":1179082,"uid":7947,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:05:29.000Z","msg":"我公司附近有幾個盤<br />\n真係每日都見證住班大陸佬大陸嬸打尖<br />\n曾經試過最仆街係原本排第五個 到架巴士黎到時可以變左第十幾個<br />\n試過同啲呀嬸講叫佢地唔好再逼 會比佢地鬧我：咁多野講有車就上啦<br />\n試過直頭有一排日日都拎住部cam影鳩住佢地<br />\n佢地就會排得好啲啲 但係就係咁屌我臭閪多事<br />\n仲話要告返我侵犯佢地私隠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都on撚9<br />\n都試過同巴士公司投訴 (扮唔同角色 eg.附近居民/附近做野既人/附近學校學生家長 etc)<br />\n叫佢地搵個人黎管理一下 (因為司機都唔撚理)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過做左以上咁多野<br />\n都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無撚用！！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"dd77d788a4f820b3bb1cd4ab10ddbc8ef6b19be8","tid":1179082,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"個次係輕鐵屌到個啊叔企係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f765dccb086692a35fb0341b23cf1724f3b4f2","tid":1179082,"uid":174502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02adb0cc640d592a4670ed78e5f5f55a35108be7","tid":1179082,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":81,"score":-80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"係咪香港人先咁鐘意爭第一第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個位啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"